channel.title: Connecting to server
channel.description:
I tryed to register my server on the server status page. It said that it must be online to be reigistered our whatever. It is running and i am online.
i went to my default gateway thing and made a new port forward. The name was my server ip, the start port was 43594, the end port was 43594, and the host port was 43594. then i saved it because there was no options left.
i also went to my firewall and created a new exception.
Name: rsps Port: 43594 TCP
what else do i need to do or what did i do wrong?
